sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Creator (Desktop/App)
    participant S as AI Sync Engine
    participant L as Organized Library

    C->>S: Saves file to "Smart Inbox"
    S->>S: Analyze: Visual context + Client history
    S-->>C: Notification: "Stored in [Client X] > [Assets] with tags: #blue, #minimalist"
    alt User disagrees
        C->>S: Manual override folder/tag
    end
    S->>L: Update Vector Index & Database
    L-->>C: Asset available for instant search